    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today? This car has been well-loved and is in really solid shape, running smoothly and looking great. It\u2019s been a total joy to drive and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
